    <h2 class="header__medium">What is particleLib?</h2>
    <div class="content-block">
      ParticleLib is a light weight utility library with basic vector functions, and basic physics functions. Theres isn't a whole lot of complexity to it. These docs may change due to the constant progress that will be happening to this library.
    </div>

    <h2 class="header__medium">Why particleLib?</h2>
    <div class="content-block">
      ParticleLib is mainly a hobby of mine. I always liked animations and wanted to dive deeper into how they worked on a more granular level. This project will likely fork into a deeper dive into a 3D library utilizing a lower level API; WebGL that give more control to the developer.
    </div>

